    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is in rougher condition and will definitely need some TLC and mechanical attention to get it back to its best. However, it's a great opportunity for someone handy looking for a bargain and a fresh start!",
