    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero swirls, chips, or imperfections in the original paint. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats are supple without a single crease, and the dash remains factory-fresh with every button providing that crisp, tactile response found only in new vehicles. Mechanically, it is flawless, supported by a comprehensive folder of every service record since day one. No stone has been left unturned in its upkeep, featuring original matching tires and a pristine undercarriage. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
